PrecisAmendment to the INCOME TAX REGULATIONS prescribing, for the purpose of the closing words in paragraph 212(1)(b), indexed debt obligations that do not provide for payments that are dependent on, or computed by reference to, the contingencies listed in those closing words, other than payments that are determined by reference to a change in the purchasing power of money.
